OL,3,CNHS board apologises after 'wrongful
OL,4,Crelease' of body discovered after
OL,5,Ccremation
OL,7,FNHS bosses have launched a full
OL,8,Finvestigation and issued an apology
OL,9,Fafter a body was wrongly released from
OL,10,Fa hospital mortuary to the undertakers
OL,11,F` with the error only discovered after
OL,12,Fcremation had taken place.
OL,14,FAs a result of the blunder, a service
OL,15,Forganised by one family to remember
OL,16,Ftheir loved one saw the wrong body
OL,17,Fcremated.
