OL,7,FNHS Greater Glasgow and Clyde
OL,8,Fconfirmed a full investigation is now
OL,9,Funder way, with staff involved
OL,10,Fsuspended while this takes place.
OL,12,FThe families affected were informed of
OL,13,Fwhat had happened, with "full support"
OL,14,Fbeing offered to them after the
OL,15,Fincident, reported to have taken place
OL,16,Flast month.
OL,18,FDr Scott Davidson, medical director at
OL,19,FNHS Greater Glasgow and Clyde, said:
OL,20,F"I would like to offer my sincere
OL,21,Fapologies to both families affected.
